SELECT *
FROM ABC400FIL.CLTMTCPF a
WHERE a.mtcclient in @{item().cbcpy_list}
AND a.mtclstdate between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd}) with UR

SELECT T1.*
FROM ABC400FIL.cnfil T1
WHERE (T1.CNTIM >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND T1.CNTIM < TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
OR T1.CNTIM = '0001-01-01 00:00:00.000000') 
AND T1.CNCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} with UR

SELECT a.* 
FROM ABC400FIL.cost_ctrs a
where a.CCTCHGDATE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart})  and   int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd}) with UR

select  T1.* 
from ABC400FIL.CP012WKF T1
WHERE T1.CWCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} 
AND T1.CHGDATE between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd}) WITH UR

SELECT *
FROM ABC400FIL.CRFILL20 a
JOIN ABC400FIL.DATECONV d ON  d.MMDDYY  = a.CRDTE
WHERE d.THE_DATE  >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND  d.THE_DATE < TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
and a.CRCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} with UR

SELECT 

CAST(T1.CRCLB as VARCHAR(6))  as CRCLB,

CAST(T1.CRMBR as VARCHAR(5))  as CRMBR,

CAST(T1.CRSEQ as VARCHAR(7))  as CRSEQ,

CAST(T1.CRDTE as VARCHAR(6))  as CRDTE,

CAST(T1.CRTIM as VARCHAR(6))  as CRTIM,

CAST(T1.CRUSR as VARCHAR(6))  as CRUSR,

CAST(T1.CRCDE as VARCHAR(3))  as CRCDE,

CAST(T1.CRTYP as VARCHAR(1))  as CRTYP,

CAST(T1.CRCHG as VARCHAR(1))  as CRCHG,

CAST(T1.CRPRT as VARCHAR(1))  as CRPRT

FROM ABC400FIL.crfil T1

--INNER JOIN ABC400FIL.cbfil T2 ON T2.CBCLB = T1.CRCLB

INNER JOIN ABC400FIL.DATECONV T3 ON MMDDYY = T1.crdte

where CRCDE = 'NEW' 

AND  T3.The_Date >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')  

AND  T3.The_Date <  TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')

AND T1.CRCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} WITH UR

SELECT T1.*
FROM (SELECT 
	CLUB_NUMBER_I
	,UPPER(TB_GRP) AS TB_GRP
	,UPPER(ABC_CODE) AS ABC_CODE
	,ORG_ACCT_DESC
	,USR_ACCT_DESC
	,ORG_ENTRY_DESC
	,USR_ENTRY_DESC
	,GLCODE
	,CRS_USER
	,CHANGE_DATE 
	,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY club_number_i,UPPER(tb_grp),upper(abc_code) ORDER BY CHANGE_DATE desc) seq
from dw3.CRS_JE_GLCODE_PREFS_TB ) T1
INNER JOIN DW.ABC400FIL_cbfil_VW T2 ON T1.CLUB_NUMBER_I = T2.CBCLB and T1.seq = 1
WHERE T1.CHANGE_DATE >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')  
AND   T1.CHANGE_DATE <  TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND T1.CLUB_NUMBER_I in @{item().cbcpy_list}

SELECT T1.*
FROM DW3.CRS_JE_REPORT_PREFS_TB T1
WHERE T1.CHANGE_DATE >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')  
AND   T1.CHANGE_DATE <  TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND T1.CLUB_NUMBER_I in @{item().cbcpy_list}

CAST(t1.CTCCTCODEC AS VARCHAR(10)) as CTCCTCODEC,   
CAST(t1.CTDTEDUEC as VARCHAR(7)) as CTDTEDUEC,
CAST(t1.CTDTEC as VARCHAR(7)) as CTDTEC,
CAST(t1.CTCENC as VARCHAR(3)) as CTCENC,
CAST(t1.CTTIMC as VARCHAR(7)) as CTTIMC,
CAST(CTUSRC AS VARCHAR(7)) as CTUSRC,
CAST(CTCDEC AS VARCHAR(8)) as CTCDEC,
CAST(CTTYPC AS VARCHAR(2)) as CTTYPC,
CAST(CTGRPC AS VARCHAR(10)) as CTGRPC,
CAST(t1.CTCTAC as VARCHAR(10)) as CTCTAC,
CAST(t1.CTSTAC as VARCHAR(10)) as CTSTAC,
CAST(t1.CTCFAC as VARCHAR(10)) as CTCFAC,
CAST(CTREFC AS VARCHAR(18)) as CTREFC,
CAST(t1.CTCBAC as VARCHAR(10)) as CTCBAC,
CAST(t1.CTCOMC as VARCHAR(8)) as CTCOMC,
CAST(t1.CTBDTC as VARCHAR(7)) as CTBDTC,
CAST(t1.CTBCHC as VARCHAR(4)) as CTBCHC,
CAST(CTR1FC AS VARCHAR(2)) as CTR1FC,
CAST(t1.CTR1SC as VARCHAR(6)) as CTR1SC,
CAST(t1.CT1DDC as VARCHAR(7)) as CT1DDC,
cast(CTDPFC as varchar(2)) as CTDPFC,
cast(CTBPFC as varchar(2)) as CTBPFC
from ABC400FIL.ctfilcctr T1 
where CTDTEC <> 0 
AND t1.CTCLBC in @{item().cbcpy_list} 
AND T1.CTDTEC >= int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) 
AND T1.CTDTEC < int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})
AND T1.CTDTEDUEC < int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})
UNION

SELECT 
CAST(C.CTHCLBNUM AS VARCHAR(5))	AS CTHCLBNUM,
CAST(C.CTHMBRNUM AS VARCHAR(5))	AS CTHMBRNUM,
CAST(C.CTHSEQNUM AS VARCHAR(5))	AS CTHSEQNUM,
CAST(C.CTHHDRUID AS VARCHAR(32)) AS CTHHDRUID,
CAST(C.CTHCURAMT AS VARCHAR(9)) AS CTHCURAMT,
CAST(C.CTHPSTAMT AS VARCHAR(9)) AS CTHPSTAMT,
CAST(C.CTHCMGAMT AS VARCHAR(9)) AS CTHCMGAMT,
CAST(C.CTHITMCNT AS VARCHAR(3)) AS CTHITMCNT,
CAST(C.CTHITMPCT AS VARCHAR(13)) AS CTHITMPCT,
CAST(C.CTHITMAMT AS VARCHAR(11)) AS CTHITMAMT
FROM ABC400FIL.CTFILCTH C 
JOIN ABC400FIL.CTFIL A ON 
A.CTCLB = C.CTHCLBNUM 
AND A.CTMBR = C.CTHMBRNUM
AND A.CTSEQ = C.CTHSEQNUM
WHERE  A.ctdte between int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowStart}) AND int(@{pipeline().parameters.windowEnd})
AND A.CTCLB in @{item().cbcpy_list} WITH UR
